          Indias Leading Provider of <span class="text-success">Turnkey Solar Solutions</span>
        </h2>
        <p>SUN24 Solution is a leading solar energy company in India, specializing in integrated solar solutions and turnkey services. Founded in 2022 by <strong>Mrs. Sweta Agnihotri</strong> and <strong>Gaurav Mishra</strong>, an IIT/ISM Dhanbad alumnus, the company is headquartered in <strong>Ahmedabad, Gujarat</strong>.</p>
        
        <p>SUN24 Solution is driven by a dynamic and entrepreneurial team, combining diverse expertise and hands-on experience in the renewable energy sector to deliver the highest quality and customized solar solutions to clients across India.</p>
        
        <p>The companys mission is to empower businesses and individuals with affordable, reliable, and sustainable solar energy solutions. SUN24 Solution helps people reduce their carbon footprint, lower energy costs, and contribute to a greener planet. Its solutions are tailored to meet the unique needs of each customer, focusing on performance, efficiency, and long-term value.</p>
        
        <p>With a customer-first approach and a passion for green energy, SUN24 Solution is dedicated to revolutionizing the way India powers its future. By making clean energy accessible and efficient, SUN24 Solution is leading the charge toward a more sustainable and energy-efficient India.</p>

